OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy with a few spots
OL,6,Fof drizzle over the hills and
OL,7,Fmountains. Occasional brighter break
OL,8,Fbut turning cloudier again later with
OL,9,Fa band of rain pushing southwards
OL,10,Facross the country from late
OL,11,Fafternoon. Less warm.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDamp this evening with rain
OL,14,Fsinking southwards. Turning drier
OL,15,Fovernight with lengthy clear skies
OL,16,Fallowing temperatures to fall. Chilly
OL,17,Fwith a touch of frost in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
