OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA chilly but fine and dry
OL,6,Fstart with sunshine. Sunshine perhaps
OL,7,Fhazier into the afternoon but
OL,8,Fremaining fine and dry. Rain arriving
OL,9,Flate evening. Feeling cooler.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FTurning
OL,12,Funsettled over the Easter weekend with
OL,13,Fshowers or longer spells of rain.
OL,14,FGenerally drier and brighter through
OL,15,FSunday. Some strong and gusty winds
OL,16,Ftoo.
